Example #1
Virtual Service to route all http traffic for my-app service to version 1

apiVersion: networking.istio.io/v1beta1
kind: VirtualService
metadata:
  name: my-app-v1
spec:
  hosts:
  - myapp.abc.com
  http:
  - name: "my-app-v1"
    route:
    - destination:
        host: service-name <my-app.my-ns.svc.cluster.local>
        subset: v1  #version of service


Example #2
Virtual Service to route 80% of traffic to v1 and 20% to v2

apiVersion: networking.istio.io/v1beta1
kind: VirtualService
metadata:
  name: my-app-v1-v2
spec:
  hosts:
  - myapp.abc.com
  gateways:
  - my-app-gateway
  http:
  - route:
    - destination:
        host: service-name <my-app.my-ns.svc.cluster.local>
        subset: v1  #version of service
      weight: 80
  - route:
    - destination: 
        host: service-name
        subset: v2
      weight: 20

Example #3 
Virtual Service to route firefox users to v2 and rest to v1

apiVersion: networking.istio.io/v1beta1
kind: VirtualService
metadata:
  name: my-app
spec:
  hosts:
  - myapp.abc.com
  http:
  - match
    - headers:
        user-agent:
          regex: '.*Firefox.*'
    route:
    - destination:
        host: service-name <my-app.my-ns.svc.cluster.local>
        subset: v2  #version of service
       
  - route:
    - destination: 
        host: service-name
        subset: v1
       

Example #4
Virtual Service which will inject a delay of 5 seconds for 80% of traffic to v2

apiVersion: networking.istio.io/v1beta1
kind: VirtualService
metadata:
  name: my-app
spec:
  hosts:
  - myapp.abc.com
  http:
  - fault:
      delay:
        fixedDelay: 5s
        percentage:
          value: 80
    route:
    - destination:
        host: service-name <my-app.my-ns.svc.cluster.local>
        subset: v2  #version of service
       
Example #5
Virtual Service which will attempt 3 times and each attempt is considered as failure if it takes more than 2 seconds

apiVersion: networking.istio.io/v1beta1
kind: VirtualService
metadata:
  name: my-app
spec:
  hosts:
  - "*"
  http:
  - route:
      - destination:
        host: service-name <my-app.my-ns.svc.cluster.local>
        subset: v2  #version of service
      retries:
        attempts: 3
        perTryTimeout: 2s


Example #6
Virtual Service which will timeout if application takes more than 10 seconds to respond

apiVersion: networking.istio.io/v1beta1
kind: VirtualService
metadata:
  name: my-app
spec:
  hosts:
  - "*"
  http:
  - route:
      - destination:
        host: service-name <my-app.my-ns.svc.cluster.local>
        subset: v2  #version of service
      timeout: 10s
